            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/DE/6C/wKgBZ1lInLmADTmyABK3f7E-oYs09.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/DE/6C/wKgBZ1lInLmADTmyABK3f7E-oYs09.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="218599844" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3517.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3517" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>孔庙和国子监
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="215560748">
            不知道有多少人和我一样，<br />
总觉得爱旅行的人多少都会喜欢喝点酒，<br />
不管是三中全会，还是偶尔咗一小口，<br />
但是总觉得在路上，<br />
如果不喝点酒好像缺了点什么。<br />
<br />
诚然旅行🀄️酒不是主角，<br />
但很多时候没有酒，<br />
会觉得整个旅行缺少了点什么，<br />
就像是朋友聚会，<br />
不喝酒氛围相对就会平淡。<br />
<br />

        </p>
