            <div id="_j_photo_218599868" data-seq="218599904" data-pid="218599868" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="4047">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7168280/218599868.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/E3/F5/wKgBZ1lIpY2AdyKmABVpQF12Feg97.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/E3/F5/wKgBZ1lIpY2AdyKmABVpQF12Feg97.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="218599868" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/4047.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="4047" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>段祺瑞执政府
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="217527189">
            一个人出去，酒算是最好的伴侣，<br />
夜里一杯红酒配电影，<br />
窝在异乡的沙发里，<br />
不会感到落寞和孤单，<br />
去见远方的朋友，酒是最真的问候，<br />
带上一瓶酒，<br />
觥筹交错推杯换盏后的互诉衷肠，<br />
会觉得格外的温暖和难忘。<br />
途中遇见小伙伴，从陌生到熟悉，<br />
酒或许就是打破生疏，<br />
拉近距离最好的催化剂。<br />
<br />
当然，酒精过敏喝不了酒另说，<br />
当然，喝多了最后故事变成了事故也另说。<br />

        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_219731367" data-seq="219731381" data-pid="219731367" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="9591134">
