                    <i class="house"></i>山峰战斗的地方
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_219731376" data-seq="219731390" data-pid="219731376" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="22330603">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7168280/219731376.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F9/2D/wKgBZ1lOCzKAC-PJAAw3if5SKl885.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F9/2D/wKgBZ1lOCzKAC-PJAAw3if5SKl885.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="219731376" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a style="cursor:default" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="22330603" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>国贸桥
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_219731379" data-seq="219731393" data-pid="219731379" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="174490">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7168280/219731379.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F9/31/wKgBZ1lOCzqAIZ_CAApdPv0Si0823.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F9/31/wKgBZ1lOCzqAIZ_CAApdPv0Si0823.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="219731379" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/174490.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="174490" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="food"></i>云·酷
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="217527386">
            刚写了开头，<br />
也给自己来了一杯朗姆酒，提提神<br />
加了薄荷叶，柠檬和雪碧。<br />
<br />
一旁的电视定格在cctv5，<br />
现场直播国足对<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11217.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="叙利亚" target="_blank">叙利亚</a>的生死之战。<br />
看完一杯酒还没喝完。<br />
最后的结果，<br />
连拿起杯子都变得沉重。<br />
<br />
拿着手机，微信群里，<br />
昔日一起看球踢球的兄弟们聊着，<br />
我说我还是喜欢贺炜解说，<br />
大白问我段暄呢？<br />
我回，早就走了。<br />
<br />
他接着说，贺炜每每解说国足都输。<br />
我说，所以最后贺炜成了贺诗人，<br />
写下了那句最慷慨激昂的——<br />
<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中国" target="_blank">中国</a>足球哪怕是再多人的痰盂，<br />
也依然是我的圣杯。<br />

        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_216719767" data-seq="216719774" data-pid="216719767" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="20309758">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7168280/216719767.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/5F/94/wKgBZ1k_gQGAY2ZJABA5nyGWhGw17.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/5F/94/wKgBZ1k_gQGAY2ZJABA5nyGWhGw17.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="216719767" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a style="cursor:default" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="20309758" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>山峰战斗的地方
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="217527458">
            贺诗人发话了，<br />
用了前一天，<br />
<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11699.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="伊朗" target="_blank">伊朗</a><a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/52314.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="亚洲" target="_blank">亚洲</a>区预选赛出线，<br />
球迷送复刻的大力神杯的话题，<br />
最后说：<br />
你生活当中达不到某种高度，<br />
你就不生活下去了吗？<br />
当然不是，你的能力到哪里，<br />
请你一定要做到你能力的上限，<br />
这样你对得起你自己。<br />
<br />
听完这话，激动了，<br />
做你能力的上限，<br />
有时候不逼自己，<br />
永远不知道自己有多牛逼。<br />
<br />
就像我每一次写游记，<br />
总会解锁一些新技能，<br />
或许不逼自己，不拿出自己能力的上限，<br />
就总会留有遗憾。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_216719769" data-seq="216719776" data-pid="216719769" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="20309758">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7168280/216719769.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/5F/9A/wKgBZ1k_gQmAfUZcABmtp9f6cJs00.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/5F/9A/wKgBZ1k_gQmAfUZcABmtp9f6cJs00.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="216719769" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a style="cursor:default" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="20309758" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>山峰战斗的地方
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_217555294" data-seq="217555295" data-pid="217555294" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="7913260">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7168280/217555294.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/24/FE/wKgBZ1lDUSGARnpbAB_XrW7KooA48.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/24/FE/wKgBZ1lDUSGARnpbAB_XrW7KooA48.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="217555294" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/7913260.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="7913260" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>双峰林场
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="217017333">
            那一刻，<br />
一大杯酒，<br />
连着柠檬直接一口干掉，<br />
一杯酒，有点酸，有点冲。<br />
<br />
那一刻，<br />
我决定把水彩本找出来，<br />
动一动好久没动的颜料和排笔，<br />
配几幅图给这样一篇游记，<br />
不辜负自己的一番苦心和执着。<br />
游记是回忆的资产，不能停。<br />
<br />
那一刻，<br />
我仿佛又回到了17年前，<br />
我拿到大学录取通知书的那天晚上，<br />
<br />
母亲做了很多菜，然后爸爸坐在桌子正中间，<br />
招呼我过去吃饭，拿了两个高脚杯，<br />
父亲给我倒了半杯红酒，<br />
这是从小到大印象中第一次父亲跟我喝酒。<br />
那一刻我也明白我要担负些什么了。<br />
<br />
都说人生就是一趟旅行，<br />
大学通知书或许就是我旅途中的第一张票据，<br />
宣告我要独自上路了。<br />
也是从那个时候起，我意识到，<br />
我的每一步成长，都离不开酒了。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_216787148" data-seq="216787149" data-pid="216787148" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="13731112">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7168280/216787148.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/39/wKgBZ1k_qtKAHGfbACETwsiH-Ag22.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/39/wKgBZ1k_qtKAHGfbACETwsiH-Ag22.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="216787148" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a style="cursor:default" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="13731112" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="food"></i>糯言酒馆
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="217017265">
            开头的最后，<br />
还是说说写这样一篇游记的初衷和想法。<br />
<br />
第一个原因，<br />
看蜂首，是我玩蚂蜂窝养成的习惯之一。<br />
每天早上上班，<br />
打开第一个网页一定是蚂蜂窝，<br />
鼠标的第一个点击一定是今天的蜂首。<br />
<br />
最近发现，蜂首开始变得不拘一格，<br />
甚至有些捉摸不定。<br />
尤其是前几日那篇<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10183.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="日本" target="_blank">日本</a>章鱼烧给我了启发。<br />
<br />
写吃的我不擅长，但是喝酒我可以啊，<br />
飘了这么多年在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>，<br />
去过的酒馆那真的是数不过来，<br />
我就写一个<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>小酒馆攻略呗？
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_215836668" data-seq="215836672" data-pid="215836668" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="22333120">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7168280/215836668.html">
