            <div id="_j_photo_274219054" data-seq="274219055" data-pid="274219054" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7168280/274219054.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:906px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/0E/76/wKgBZ1o05--ADnJQAAX9EiNPrvg19.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/0E/76/wKgBZ1o05--ADnJQAAX9EiNPrvg19.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="274219054" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="217543845">
            第二个原因，<br />
很多外地朋友来到<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>，找到我，<br />
还是看中了我在这里生活了十几年，<br />
或者干脆觉得我就是个老<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>大爷，<br />
<br />
街道办大爷身份不假，<br />
不过还真是个漂在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>的异乡人。<br />
但这丝毫不影响我来推荐深度游，<br />
想和一座城市发生化学反应，<br />
那就去它的夜里走一走，<br />
大排档，胡同口，小院里，酒馆里，<br />
去看看它最真实的一面。<br />

        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_216126635" data-seq="216126645" data-pid="216126635" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="22333120">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7168280/216126635.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:477px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/C2/31/wKgBZ1k8x_-AfNRCABP-NDHlZ9I06.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/C2/31/wKgBZ1k8x_-AfNRCABP-NDHlZ9I06.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="216126635" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a style="cursor:default" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="22333120" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>hoper
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="217533172">
            再有一个原因，<br />
提到酒，便会想起一句话：<br />
愿孤独的人都有酒喝，<br />
流浪的人都会唱歌。<br />
这是我写给大家明信片上的一句。<br />
<br />
身处这个时代， 我们大多数人疲于奔命，<br />
只顾着远方而忽略了当下。<br />
其实，正如喜欢的那首歌：<br />
生活不只有眼前的苟且，<br />
还有诗和远方的田野。<br />
 生活在疏离感倍增的城市中，<br />
太多人带着面具，<br />
在社会中扮演成熟与精明。<br />
就从这一点上看，我们都是孤独的。<br />
我从04年来到这座城市，<br />
酒一直陪伴着我，<br />
把我的真实、真诚、脆弱和豪迈演绎得淋漓尽致。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_216126638" data-seq="216126648" data-pid="216126638" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="22333120">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7168280/216126638.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/C2/34/wKgBZ1k8yASAJfMGAAuzWoeUI0k99.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/C2/34/wKgBZ1k8yASAJfMGAAuzWoeUI0k99.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="216126638" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a style="cursor:default" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="22333120" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>hoper
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_216126641" data-seq="216126651" data-pid="216126641" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="22333120">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7168280/216126641.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:455px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/C2/38/wKgBZ1k8yAqARbxtAA4Or0vfkkM84.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/C2/38/wKgBZ1k8yAqARbxtAA4Or0vfkkM84.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="216126641" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a style="cursor:default" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="22333120" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>hoper
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="219805935">
            其实，我也知道，<br />
酒不是解决问题的唯一途径，<br />
但它就和麻药一样，<br />
绝对是来的最快的。<br />
与君初相识，似是故人来。<br />
就是这个效果。<br />
<br />
所以码一篇文字，跟酒有关，<br />
跟旅行有关，跟这座城市有关。<br />
推荐一些有意思的小酒馆和一些深度周边游的地方，<br />
接地气，有风格，且温暖，<br />
但愿你能在安静小酌里，<br />
喝出源自灵魂深处的真实人情味。<br />

        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_220200819" data-seq="220200825" data-pid="220200819" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="13061333">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7168280/220200819.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:599px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/3C/D5/wKgBZ1lQVxCAA2vQABN7NehsKwU87.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/3C/D5/wKgBZ1lQVxCAA2vQABN7NehsKwU87.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="220200819" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a style="cursor:default" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="13061333" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="food"></i>赋格
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div data-seq="215573975" data-index="1" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t1"><span class="_j_anchor">嗯哼一声</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="219201223">
            认识我的人都说峰哥江湖，<br />
再熟一点的人都说峰哥情怀，<br />
再近一点点，就都会说我的人生三大爱好：<br />
抽烟喝酒烫头。<br />
<br />
我来到这座城市已经是第十三个年头，<br />
从2004年毕业，一直到现在，<br />
虽然陆陆续续曾经在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10466.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="长沙" target="_blank">长沙</a>上过几年学，<br />
但是上学期间依旧会经常回家。<br />
<br />
在一座城市生活久了，漂泊久了，<br />
很多时候发现它最烟火气的时候，<br />
莫过于清晨的胡同巷子口<br />
和夜晚的大排档或者小酒馆。<br />
<br />
记得去年，有那么一段流行一句话——<br />
我有故事，你有酒么？<br />
冥冥中把酒和故事捆绑在了一起。<br />
也确实如此，没有酒的时候，<br />
我们总是显得很内敛。<br />
于是乎，几个旅行故事，<br />
便成了最好的下酒菜。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_216367911" data-seq="216367912" data-pid="216367911" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="2530432">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7168280/216367911.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:680px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/3E/E9/wKgBZ1k97i6ARrLcABSYm5nnMvc87.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/3E/E9/wKgBZ1k97i6ARrLcABSYm5nnMvc87.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="216367911" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/2530432.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="2530432" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="play"></i>小酒馆
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="217527234">
            最主要的是之前写游记，<br />
一直以一个游客的角色去到一个地方，<br />
去感受一个新环境，这次不同，<br />
第44篇游记，以主人的身份，<br />
或者说以一个邀请者的身份，<br />
来带大家深度逛逛<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>这座城。<br />
<br />
几点说明，写在前面：<br />
<br />
一是特别感谢给我提供故事的朋友们，<br />
逼格宝，威士忌，南方姑娘，梅子，郭一，Daniel&nbsp;，贩暖，介绍贩暖的玎玎，<br />
小马驹，妮儿坨坨，艳艳，<br />
我不生产故事，我只是故事的搬运工。<br />
<br />
在这深表感谢，峰哥的酒是欠下了，<br />
等着你们来<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>兑现，不醉不回。<br />
<br />
二是这篇游记，算是一个整理，<br />
生活中日常累积的整理，<br />
多数照片为手机拍摄，画质确实有点渣。<br />
很多酒馆的照片都没有放门面，<br />
给大家留个幻想，也避免打广告之嫌。<br />
<br />
三要感谢夏凉姑娘，<br />
感谢待着，一个曾经陪伴我生活，<br />
现在却已经消失的网站，<br />
没有她们，我永远不会知道，<br />
有这么多生活的另一种可能。<br />
<br />
另外文中很多故事为朋友提供，<br />
所以配图都是过往一些累积的照片，<br />
特别是姑娘别对号入座，<br />
因为都是宝马车插奔驰标，<br />
不是原配。<br />
<br />
最后文中所有我主观的总结的话语，<br />
或者祝愿，都送给你。<br />
现在想想或许心痛，<br />
但又觉得，最后的相见真的很美好。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_220198079" data-seq="220198080" data-pid="220198079" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="20309758">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7168280/220198079.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:830px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/3B/46/wKgBZ1lQTS-ADQL7AAsxbY1_EkU58.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/3B/46/wKgBZ1lQTS-ADQL7AAsxbY1_EkU58.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="220198079" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a style="cursor:default" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="20309758" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>山峰战斗的地方
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_216957702" data-seq="216957703" data-pid="216957702" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="20309758">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_7168280/216957702.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:1020px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/74/D8/wKgBZ1lAoVOAUNX_AAv1kd24AlI18.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/74/D8/wKgBZ1lAoVOAUNX_AAv1kd24AlI18.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="216957702" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a style="cursor:default" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="20309758" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>山峰战斗的地方
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
    
